Understood on your disengagement. We have your materials on file, and if a future analytics engineering / product analytics opening comes up that’s a closer match, we’ll reach out using the information you shared.

Wishing you the best with the rest of your search. [TALK]
conversation.thought: Seeker_E is on Company_A’s true priority list but low (4/5) and has already been rejected multiple times with clear closure communicated. In round 30 there’s no opportunity to engage higher-priority seekers (Seeker_B or Seeker_D) via incoming messages, and Seeker_E is not applying—only disengaging. Given the history, the consistent decision is to maintain closure and respond politely with [TALK].
